The paper deals with privacy mechanisms and mutual information, which are common topics in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of utility metrics and tradeoff problems suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and optimization (cs.DS). Finally, the emphasis on privacy and information leakage may also place the paper in the sub-category of security and privacy (cs.SI).
